info.author: Andrew C. Bulhak
info.description:
ProfilingProxy is a proxy class for profiling method calls of objects. A
ProfilingProxy object wraps an existing object, intercepts calls to its methods
and records method execution times, including inter-method call graphs and
calling time breakdowns.
